Category:Imperial Intelligence personnel of the resurgent Sith Empire

nodes.text: "Deadfall" was the callsign of a notorious Human male agent in the employ of the Sith Empire. Deadfall specialized in subterfuge, creating chaos on planets in advance of an Imperial invasion. Havoc Squad attacked Outpost Shadowstrike on Voss hoping to capture him, but Deadfall died in the resulting conflict.
